OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779217874
OL,3,CNHS boss probed on emails where he was
OL,4,C'fed up' of Nottingham inquiry
OL,6,FThe Nottingham Inquiry has today heard
OL,7,Ffrom the chief executive of the NHS
OL,8,Ftrust that treated Valdo Calocane that
OL,9,Fthere were clear issues around risk
OL,10,Fassessment, years before the attack.
OL,12,FCalocane was in the care of the trust
OL,13,Ftwo years before he went on to kill
OL,14,Fthree people, and injure three others
OL,15,Fin the city in 2023.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779217874
OL,3,CNHS boss probed on emails where he was
OL,4,C'fed up' of Nottingham inquiry
OL,6,FHead of Psychiatric Services for
OL,7,FNottinghamshire Healthcare NHS
OL,8,FFoundation Trust Ifti Majid was head
OL,9,Fof mental health services when the
OL,10,Fattacks happened, but he had only been
OL,11,Fin place for six months at the time.
OL,13,FHe was asked by Rachel Langdale KC
OL,14,Fabout the risks surrounding Calocane:
OL,15,F"Staff were doing visits in any case
OL,16,Fin a combination for their own safety.
OL,17,FBefore then had you heard of that in
OL,18,Fany other case?"
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779217874
OL,3,CNHS boss probed on emails where he was
OL,4,C'fed up' of Nottingham inquiry
OL,6,FHe replied: "Not as I recall
OL,7,Fspecifically but it's not uncommon
OL,8,Fpractice."
OL,10,FMajid was then asked "Would you have
OL,11,Fseen that as a risk to other members
OL,12,Fof the public as well as care
OL,13,Fprofessionals if you deemed it
OL,14,Fnecessary for two people to visit VC
OL,15,Fat that point?"
OL,17,FHe responded that "I would expect as
OL,18,Fpart of the explanation of that action
OL,19,Fthat risk of violence or whatever it
OL,20,Fwas would extend beyond just staff."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779217874
OL,3,CNHS boss probed on emails where he was
OL,4,C'fed up' of Nottingham inquiry
OL,6,FUniversity of Nottingham students
OL,7,FGrace O'Malley-Kumar and Barnaby
OL,8,FWebber died in the attack, along with
OL,9,F65-year-old school caretaker Ian
OL,10,FCoates.
OL,12,F"Fed up" with needing to do the inquiry
OL,14,FMr Majid also defended an email he
OL,15,Fsent to staff in which he said he was
OL,16,F"fed up" as he prepared for the
OL,17,FNottingham Inquiry.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779217874
OL,3,CNHS boss probed on emails where he was
OL,4,C'fed up' of Nottingham inquiry
OL,6,FHe was was asked to explain what he
OL,7,Fmeant in an email to around 11,000
OL,8,Fstaff sent in October last year which
OL,9,Fread:
OL,11,F"Along with many colleagues in our
OL,12,Ftrust I now have to respond to a very
OL,13,Fdetailed Nottingham Inquiry rule 9
OL,14,F(set of legal questions) within a set
OL,15,Ftimescale and I am so sorry, but this
OL,16,Fmeans that many of the sessions I have
OL,17,Fhad planned to come out to teams and
OL,18,Fservices need to be postponed.
OL,20,F"I am fed up with needing to do this,
OL,21,Fbut I am afraid needs must."
OL,26,@}D@\O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779217874
OL,3,CNHS boss probed on emails where he was
OL,4,C'fed up' of Nottingham inquiry
OL,6,FMr Majid said he wanted to make it
OL,7,F"absolutely clear" that he recognised
OL,8,Fthe importance of the inquiry process,
OL,9,Fwhich is examining events leading up
OL,10,Fto the killings.
OL,12,FHe said: "When I am talking about
OL,13,Fbeing fed up, I am talking about being
OL,14,Ffed up with letting colleagues down by
OL,15,Fneeding to cancel clinical visits.
OL,17,F"The reason for that is that clinical
OL,18,Fvisits are a really important way of
OL,19,Fengagement and escalation.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@RO]tD@JOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779217874
OL,3,CNHS boss probed on emails where he was
OL,4,C'fed up' of Nottingham inquiry
OL,6,F"I want to make it absolutely clear
OL,7,Fthat in no way am I talking about
OL,8,Fbeing fed up with the inquiry and
OL,9,Frecognise the importance of the
OL,10,Finquiry, but also... I recognise how
OL,11,Fhard colleagues work to meet the needs
OL,12,Fof the inquiry and I think it is
OL,13,Fimportant I recognise them for doing
OL,14,Fthat."
OL,16,FMr Majid is due to retire in June.
OL,18,F"There was clearly an issue with risk
OL,19,Fassessments"
OL,26,@vD@FO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779217874
OL,3,CNHS boss probed on emails where he was
OL,4,C'fed up' of Nottingham inquiry
OL,6,FMr. Majid's predecessor, Dr. John
OL,7,FBrewin, also gave evidence at the
OL,8,Finquiry.
OL,10,FHe was in charge of mental health
OL,11,Fservices at the trust while they were
OL,12,Fcaring for Calocane, and admitted
OL,13,Ftoday that he thought the team took
OL,14,F'insufficient steps' when asked about
OL,15,Fmanaging risk.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779217874
OL,3,CNHS boss probed on emails where he was
OL,4,C'fed up' of Nottingham inquiry
OL,6,FQuestioned by Inquiry Counsel Craig
OL,7,FCarr, Dr. Brewin was asked about CQC
OL,8,F(Care Quality Commission) report from
OL,9,F2019, around the start of the period
OL,10,Fof his leadership. It found risk
OL,11,Fmanagement at the trust was
OL,12,F'inadequate'.
OL,14,FHe said "I was somewhat surprised at
OL,15,Fthe level of concern the CQC had
OL,16,Ffound, and that's not a good position
OL,17,Fto be in. You like to think that you
OL,18,Fknow where things are, but this was
OL,19,Fclearly a signal early in my tenure
OL,20,Fthat this was not the case."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779217874
OL,3,CNHS boss probed on emails where he was
OL,4,C'fed up' of Nottingham inquiry
OL,6,FAsked about a further CQC report from
OL,7,F2020 found that risk management at the
OL,8,Ftrust was still 'inadequate', Dr.
OL,9,FBrewin said the context of the 'huge
OL,10,Fchange' brought by the covid pandemic
OL,11,Fat the time was an important to keep
OL,12,Fin mind.
OL,14,F"There were some positive statements
OL,15,Fabout the staffing on the ward being
OL,16,Fadequate, the environments were clean
OL,17,Fand well-kept.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779217874
OL,3,CNHS boss probed on emails where he was
OL,4,C'fed up' of Nottingham inquiry
OL,6,F"There was a sense that despite
OL,7,Feverything the pandemic had thrown at
OL,8,Fus we were starting to lay the
OL,9,Ffoundation for changes. There was
OL,10,Fcertainly no sense of complacency.
OL,12,F"The improvement plan I was trying to
OL,13,Froll out would take a minimum of three
OL,14,For four years."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779217874
OL,3,CNHS boss probed on emails where he was
OL,4,C'fed up' of Nottingham inquiry
OL,6,FMr Carr then referred to a 2022 CQC
OL,7,Freport which had concerns about risk
OL,8,Fassessments asking "Is that something
OL,9,Fwhich is effected by covid, having
OL,10,Frisk assessments which were not
OL,11,Fcomplete, or comprehensive, isn't the
OL,12,Fissue a more fundamental one?"
OL,14,FDr. Brewin responded: "I'm not
OL,15,Fsuggesting that covid was the only
OL,16,Freason for this. There was clearly an
OL,17,Fissue with full risk assessments, and
OL,18,Fdoing full risk assessments to the
OL,19,Fstandard of national guidance yes."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779217874
OL,3,CNHS boss probed on emails where he was
OL,4,C'fed up' of Nottingham inquiry
OL,6,FHe was also asked about the trusts
OL,7,Frelationship with the police in
OL,8,Frelation to a previous incident in
OL,9,F2020 when Calocane had tried to kicked
OL,10,Fa woman's door, scaring her into
OL,11,Fjumping out of a window.
OL,13,FDr. Brewin accepted that there had
OL,14,Fbeen a 'failure to report a serious
OL,15,Fincident' at the time, and asked if
OL,16,Fthis 'reflected poor oversight at the
OL,17,Fexecutive level or by the serious
OL,18,Fincident group' he admitted 'it would
OL,19,Fsuggest that yes.'
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779217874
OL,3,CNHS boss probed on emails where he was
OL,4,C'fed up' of Nottingham inquiry
OL,6,FHis successor Mr Majid said that he
OL,7,Fdidn't believe the trust has been in
OL,8,Fcontact with her to offer an apology
OL,9,Fyet, but said "it's something that we
OL,10,Fneed to look to do."
OL,12,F"Threatened with closure"
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G14/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779217874
OL,3,CNHS boss probed on emails where he was
OL,4,C'fed up' of Nottingham inquiry
OL,6,FThe inquiry was shown an email Mr
OL,7,FBrewin had sent on October 29 2021
OL,8,Ffollowing a meeting with three ward
OL,9,Fmanagers at Highbury Hospital in
OL,10,FNottingham, where Calocane was
OL,11,Fdetained under mental health laws on
OL,12,Ffour occasions between 2020 and 2022,
OL,13,Fin which he feared the hospital could
OL,14,Fbe threatened with closure if
OL,15,Fimprovements were not made.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G15/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37416
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779217874
OL,3,CNHS boss probed on emails where he was
OL,4,C'fed up' of Nottingham inquiry
OL,6,FHis email said he had "had a very
OL,7,Fsobering and at times harrowing
OL,8,Fconversation about their concerns",
OL,9,Fadding: "They were professional,
OL,10,Fcommitted and passionate about doing
OL,11,Fthe right thing... we have reached a
OL,12,Fpoint where the services are not safe
OL,13,Fand we need an immediate response to
OL,14,Fhelp support them.
OL,16,F"There is a sense of despondency that
OL,17,Fdespite flagging this since at least
OL,18,FJune, nothing has happened.
OL,20,F"And that if CQC arrived, we would be
OL,21,Fthreatened with closure."
OL,26,@nD@WOUpD@bO]qD@IOUxD@AOU|D@AOU}D@YO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G16/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37417
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779217874
OL,3,CNHS boss probed on emails where he was
OL,4,C'fed up' of Nottingham inquiry
OL,6,FAsked by counsel to the enquiry Craig
OL,7,FCarr what the basis of the managers'
OL,8,Fconcerns were, Mr Brewin said: "The
OL,9,Fgeneral thrust of their concern and
OL,10,Fthis call to arms was related to
OL,11,Fstaffing and having adequately
OL,12,Fqualified and experienced senior staff
OL,13,Fon the wards, that the more senior
OL,14,Fstaff on the wards were compromised in
OL,15,Ftheir ability to spend time on the
OL,16,Fward due to other tasks they had."
OL,26,@pD@`OUxD@bO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G17/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37418
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779217874
OL,3,CNHS boss probed on emails where he was
OL,4,C'fed up' of Nottingham inquiry
OL,6,FHe also said there were concerns about
OL,7,Fan "overemphasis" on the use of agency
OL,8,Fstaff and a "sense of exhaustion" at
OL,9,Fhaving to work in this way with an
OL,10,Finpatient population of patients who
OL,11,Fwere "probably more unwell than prior
OL,12,Fto the pandemic due to perhaps delays
OL,13,Fin getting access to treatment".
OL,15,FThe inquiry continues.
OL,26,@oD@DOUoD@QO]pD@MOUpD@aO]sD@FOUuD@_O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G18/19
